sequenceDiagram
   participant Student
   participant FocusTimeSystem
   participant TimerService
   participant NotificationService


   Student->>FocusTimeSystem: Start Focus Session Request
   activate FocusTimeSystem
   FocusTimeSystem->>Student: Display Session Options
   Student->>FocusTimeSystem: Select Duration & Start
   FocusTimeSystem->>TimerService: Initialize Timer
   activate TimerService
   TimerService-->>FocusTimeSystem: Timer Started
   deactivate TimerService
   FocusTimeSystem->>NotificationService: Schedule Focus Notifications
   activate NotificationService
   NotificationService-->>FocusTimeSystem: Notifications Scheduled
   deactivate NotificationService
   FocusTimeSystem-->>Student: Confirm Session Start
   deactivate FocusTimeSystem
